vernac_cmds: Require Import Bool BinPos Orders OrdersEx MSetInterface.
Module PositiveSet <: S with Module E:=PositiveOrderedTypeBits.
Inductive tree := | Leaf : tree | Node : tree -> bool -> tree -> tree.
Scheme tree_ind := Induction for tree Sort Prop.
Fixpoint is_empty (m : t) : bool := match m with | Leaf => true | Node l b r => negb b &&& is_empty l &&& is_empty r end.
Fixpoint mem (i : positive) (m : t) {struct m} : bool := match m with | Leaf => false | Node l o r => match i with | 1 => o | i~0 => mem i l | i~1 => mem i r end end.

Fixpoint add (i : positive) (m : t) : t := match m with | Leaf => match i with | 1 => Node Leaf true Leaf | i~0 => Node (add i Leaf) false Leaf | i~1 => Node Leaf false (add i Leaf) end | Node l o r => match i with | 1 => Node l true r | i~0 => Node (add i l) o r | i~1 => Node l o (add i r) end end.
Definition singleton i := add i empty.
Definition node (l : t) (b: bool) (r : t) : t := if b then Node l b r else match l,r with | Leaf,Leaf => Leaf | _,_ => Node l false r end.

Fixpoint remove (i : positive) (m : t) {struct m} : t := match m with | Leaf => Leaf | Node l o r => match i with | 1 => node l false r | i~0 => node (remove i l) o r | i~1 => node l o (remove i r) end end.
Fixpoint union (m m': t) : t := match m with | Leaf => m' | Node l o r => match m' with | Leaf => m | Node l' o' r' => Node (union l l') (o||o') (union r r') end end.
Fixpoint inter (m m': t) : t := match m with | Leaf => Leaf | Node l o r => match m' with | Leaf => Leaf | Node l' o' r' => node (inter l l') (o&&o') (inter r r') end end.
Fixpoint diff (m m': t) : t := match m with | Leaf => Leaf | Node l o r => match m' with | Leaf => m | Node l' o' r' => node (diff l l') (o&&negb o') (diff r r') end end.
Fixpoint equal (m m': t): bool := match m with | Leaf => is_empty m' | Node l o r => match m' with | Leaf => is_empty m | Node l' o' r' => eqb o o' &&& equal l l' &&& equal r r' end end.
Fixpoint subset (m m': t): bool := match m with | Leaf => true | Node l o r => match m' with | Leaf => is_empty m | Node l' o' r' => (negb o ||| o') &&& subset l l' &&& subset r r' end end.
Fixpoint rev_append (y x : elt) : elt := match y with | 1 => x | y~1 => rev_append y x~1 | y~0 => rev_append y x~0 end.
Fixpoint xfold (m : t) (v : B) (i : positive) := match m with | Leaf => v | Node l true r => xfold r (f (rev i) (xfold l v i~0)) i~1 | Node l false r => xfold r (xfold l v i~0) i~1 end.
Definition fold m i := xfold m i 1.
Fixpoint xforall (m : t) (i : positive) := match m with | Leaf => true | Node l o r => (negb o ||| f (rev i)) &&& xforall r i~1 &&& xforall l i~0 end.
Fixpoint xexists (m : t) (i : positive) := match m with | Leaf => false | Node l o r => (o &&& f (rev i)) ||| xexists r i~1 ||| xexists l i~0 end.
Fixpoint xfilter (m : t) (i : positive) : t := match m with | Leaf => Leaf | Node l o r => node (xfilter l i~0) (o &&& f (rev i)) (xfilter r i~1) end.

Fixpoint xpartition (m : t) (i : positive) : t * t := match m with | Leaf => (Leaf,Leaf) | Node l o r => let (lt,lf) := xpartition l i~0 in let (rt,rf) := xpartition r i~1 in if o then let fi := f (rev i) in (node lt fi rt, node lf (negb fi) rf) else (node lt false rt, node lf false rf) end.

Fixpoint xelements (m : t) (i : positive) (a: list positive) := match m with | Leaf => a | Node l false r => xelements l i~0 (xelements r i~1 a) | Node l true r => xelements l i~0 (rev i :: xelements r i~1 a) end.
Definition elements (m : t) := xelements m 1 nil.
Fixpoint cardinal (m : t) : nat := match m with | Leaf => O | Node l false r => (cardinal l + cardinal r)%nat | Node l true r => S (cardinal l + cardinal r) end.
Fixpoint choose (m: t) : option elt := match m with | Leaf => None | Node l o r => if o then Some 1 else match choose l with | None => option_map xI (choose r) | Some i => Some i~0 end end.
Fixpoint min_elt (m: t) : option elt := match m with | Leaf => None | Node l o r => match min_elt l with | None => if o then Some 1 else option_map xI (min_elt r) | Some i => Some i~0 end end.
Fixpoint max_elt (m: t) : option elt := match m with | Leaf => None | Node l o r => match max_elt r with | None => if o then Some 1 else option_map xO (max_elt l) | Some i => Some i~1 end end.
Notation lex u v := match u with Eq => v | Lt => Lt | Gt => Gt end.
Definition compare_bool a b := match a,b with | false, true => Lt | true, false => Gt | _,_ => Eq end.

Fixpoint compare (m m': t): comparison := match m,m' with | Leaf,_ => if is_empty m' then Eq else Lt | _,Leaf => if is_empty m then Eq else Gt | Node l o r,Node l' o' r' => lex (compare_bool o o') (lex (compare l l') (compare r r')) end.
Definition In i t := mem i t = true.
Definition Equal s s' := forall a : elt, In a s <-> In a s'.
Definition Subset s s' := forall a : elt, In a s -> In a s'.
Definition Empty s := forall a : elt, ~ In a s.
Definition For_all (P : elt -> Prop) s := forall x, In x s -> P x.
Definition Exists (P : elt -> Prop) s := exists x, In x s /\ P x.
Notation "s [=] t" := (Equal s t) (at level 70, no associativity).
Notation "s [<=] t" := (Subset s t) (at level 70, no associativity).
Definition lt m m' := compare m m' = Lt.
intros s s' Hs x x' Hx.
Lemma mem_spec: forall s x, mem x s = true <-> In x s.
Lemma mem_Leaf: forall x, mem x Leaf = false.
Lemma mem_node: forall x l o r, mem x (node l o r) = mem x (Node l o r).
Lemma is_empty_spec: forall s, is_empty s = true <-> Empty s.
induction s as [|l IHl o r IHr]; simpl.
intros H [a|a|]; apply H || intro; discriminate.
Lemma subset_Leaf_s: forall s, Leaf [<=] s.
Lemma subset_spec: forall s s', subset s s' = true <-> s [<=] s'.
induction s as [|l IHl o r IHr]; intros [|l' o' r']; simpl.
destruct i; destruct H as [[H Hl] Hr].
Lemma equal_subset: forall s s', equal s s' = subset s s' && subset s' s.
induction s as [|l IHl o r IHr]; intros [|l' o' r']; simpl; trivial.
Lemma equal_spec: forall s s', equal s s' = true <-> Equal s s'.
Lemma eq_dec : forall s s', { eq s s' } + { ~ eq s s' }.
Lemma lex_Opp: forall u v u' v', u = CompOpp u' -> v = CompOpp v' -> lex u v = CompOpp (lex u' v').
Lemma compare_bool_inv: forall b b', compare_bool b b' = CompOpp (compare_bool b' b).
Lemma compare_inv: forall s s', compare s s' = CompOpp (compare s' s).
induction s as [|l IHl o r IHr]; destruct s' as [|l' o' r']; trivial.
case compare_bool; simpl; trivial; apply lex_Opp; auto.
Lemma lex_Eq: forall u v, lex u v = Eq <-> u=Eq /\ v=Eq.
intros u v; destruct u; intuition discriminate.
Lemma compare_bool_Eq: forall b1 b2, compare_bool b1 b2 = Eq <-> eqb b1 b2 = true.
Lemma compare_equal: forall s s', compare s s' = Eq <-> equal s s' = true.
induction s as [|l IHl o r IHr]; destruct s' as [|l' o' r'].
Lemma compare_gt: forall s s', compare s s' = Gt -> lt s' s.
Lemma compare_eq: forall s s', compare s s' = Eq -> eq s s'.
Lemma compare_spec : forall s s' : t, CompSpec eq lt s s' (compare s s').
case_eq (compare s s'); intro H; constructor.

Inductive ct: comparison -> comparison -> comparison -> Prop := | ct_xxx: forall x, ct x x x | ct_xex: forall x, ct x Eq x | ct_exx: forall x, ct Eq x x | ct_glx: forall x, ct Gt Lt x | ct_lgx: forall x, ct Lt Gt x.
Lemma ct_cxe: forall x, ct (CompOpp x) x Eq.
Lemma ct_xce: forall x, ct x (CompOpp x) Eq.
Lemma ct_lxl: forall x, ct Lt x Lt.
Lemma ct_gxg: forall x, ct Gt x Gt.
Lemma ct_xll: forall x, ct x Lt Lt.
Lemma ct_xgg: forall x, ct x Gt Gt.
Local Hint Resolve ct_cxe ct_xce ct_lxl ct_xll ct_gxg ct_xgg: ct.
Lemma ct_lex: forall u v w u' v' w', ct u v w -> ct u' v' w' -> ct (lex u u') (lex v v') (lex w w').
intros u v w u' v' w' H H'.
inversion_clear H; inversion_clear H'; ct; destruct w; ct; destruct w'; ct.
Lemma ct_compare_bool: forall a b c, ct (compare_bool a b) (compare_bool b c) (compare_bool a c).
Lemma compare_x_Leaf: forall s, compare s Leaf = if is_empty s then Eq else Gt.
Lemma compare_empty_x: forall a, is_empty a = true -> forall b, compare a b = if is_empty b then Eq else Lt.
induction a as [|l IHl o r IHr]; trivial.
destruct b as [|l' [|] r']; simpl compare; trivial.
Lemma compare_x_empty: forall a, is_empty a = true -> forall b, compare b a = if is_empty b then Eq else Gt.
Lemma ct_compare: forall a b c, ct (compare a b) (compare b c) (compare a c).
induction a as [|l IHl o r IHr]; intros s' s''.
destruct s' as [|l' o' r']; destruct s'' as [|l'' o'' r'']; ct.
case_eq (is_empty (Node l' o' r')); intro H'.
case_eq (is_empty (Node l'' o'' r'')); intro H''.
destruct s' as [|l' o' r']; destruct s'' as [|l'' o'' r''].
case_eq (is_empty (Node l o r)); intro H.
case_eq (is_empty (Node l'' o'' r'')); intro H''.
case_eq (is_empty (Node l o r)); intro H.
case_eq (is_empty (Node l' o' r')); intro H'.

Lemma add_spec: forall s x y, In y (add x s) <-> y=x \/ In y s.
intros s x y; revert x y s.
induction x; intros [y|y|] [|l o r]; simpl mem; try (rewrite IHx; clear IHx); rewrite ?mem_Leaf; intuition congruence.
Lemma remove_spec: forall s x y, In y (remove x s) <-> In y s /\ y<>x.
intros s x y; revert x y s.
induction x; intros [y|y|] [|l o r]; simpl remove; rewrite ?mem_node; simpl mem; try (rewrite IHx; clear IHx); rewrite ?mem_Leaf; intuition congruence.
Lemma singleton_spec : forall x y, In y (singleton x) <-> y=x.
Lemma union_spec: forall s s' x, In x (union s s') <-> In x s \/ In x s'.
intros s s' x; revert x s s'.
induction x; destruct s; destruct s'; simpl union; simpl mem; try (rewrite IHx; clear IHx); try intuition congruence.
Lemma inter_spec: forall s s' x, In x (inter s s') <-> In x s /\ In x s'.
intros s s' x; revert x s s'.
induction x; destruct s; destruct s'; simpl inter; rewrite ?mem_node; simpl mem; try (rewrite IHx; clear IHx); try intuition congruence.
Lemma diff_spec: forall s s' x, In x (diff s s') <-> In x s /\ ~ In x s'.
intros s s' x; revert x s s'.
induction x; destruct s; destruct s' as [|l' o' r']; simpl diff; rewrite ?mem_node; simpl mem; try (rewrite IHx; clear IHx); try intuition congruence.
Lemma fold_spec: forall s (A : Type) (i : A) (f : elt -> A -> A), fold f s i = fold_left (fun a e => f e a) (elements s) i.
set (f' := fun a e => f e a).
assert (H: forall s i j acc, fold_left f' acc (xfold f s i j) = fold_left f' (xelements s j acc) i).
induction s as [|l IHl o r IHr]; intros; trivial.
destruct o; simpl xelements; simpl xfold.
Lemma cardinal_spec: forall s, cardinal s = length (elements s).
assert (H: forall s j acc, (cardinal s + length acc)%nat = length (xelements s j acc)).
induction s as [|l IHl b r IHr]; intros j acc; simpl; trivial.
Lemma xfilter_spec: forall f s x i, In x (xfilter f s i) <-> In x s /\ f (i@x) = true.
induction s as [|l IHl o r IHr]; intros x i; simpl xfilter.
Lemma filter_spec: forall s x f, @compat_bool elt E.eq f -> (In x (filter f s) <-> In x s /\ f x = true).
Lemma xforall_spec: forall f s i, xforall f s i = true <-> For_all (fun x => f (i@x) = true) s.
induction s as [|l IHl o r IHr]; intros i; simpl.
Lemma for_all_spec: forall s f, @compat_bool elt E.eq f -> (for_all f s = true <-> For_all (fun x => f x = true) s).
Lemma xexists_spec: forall f s i, xexists f s i = true <-> Exists (fun x => f (i@x) = true) s.
induction s as [|l IHl o r IHr]; intros i; simpl.
Lemma exists_spec : forall s f, @compat_bool elt E.eq f -> (exists_ f s = true <-> Exists (fun x => f x = true) s).
Lemma partition_filter : forall s f, partition f s = (filter f s, filter (fun x => negb (f x)) s).
induction s as [|l IHl o r IHr]; intro j.
destruct o; simpl; rewrite IHl, IHr; reflexivity.
Lemma partition_spec1 : forall s f, @compat_bool elt E.eq f -> Equal (fst (partition f s)) (filter f s).
Lemma partition_spec2 : forall s f, @compat_bool elt E.eq f -> Equal (snd (partition f s)) (filter (fun x => negb (f x)) s).
Lemma xelements_spec: forall s j acc y, InL y (xelements s j acc) <-> InL y acc \/ exists x, y=(j@x) /\ mem x s = true.
induction s as [|l IHl o r IHr]; simpl.
Lemma elements_spec1: forall s x, InL x (elements s) <-> In x s.
split; [ intros [A|(y & B & C)] | intros IN ].
Lemma lt_rev_append: forall j x y, E.lt x y -> E.lt (j@x) (j@y).
Lemma elements_spec2: forall s, sort E.lt (elements s).
assert (H: forall s j acc, sort E.lt acc -> (forall x y, In x s -> InL y acc -> E.lt (j@x) y) -> sort E.lt (xelements s j acc)).
induction s as [|l IHl o r IHr]; simpl; trivial.
assert (H': InL z (xelements r j~1 acc)).
Lemma elements_spec2w: forall s, NoDupA E.eq (elements s).
apply SortA_NoDupA with E.lt; auto with *.
Lemma choose_spec1: forall s x, choose s = Some x -> In x s.
induction s as [| l IHl o r IHr]; simpl.
Lemma choose_spec2: forall s, choose s = None -> Empty s.
induction s as [|l IHl o r IHr].
Lemma choose_empty: forall s, is_empty s = true -> choose s = None.
Lemma choose_spec3': forall s s', Equal s s' -> choose s = choose s'.
induction s as [|l IHl o r IHr].
generalize (Node l o r) as s.
Lemma choose_spec3: forall s s' x y, choose s = Some x -> choose s' = Some y -> Equal s s' -> E.eq x y.
intros s s' x y Hx Hy H.
Lemma min_elt_spec1: forall s x, min_elt s = Some x -> In x s.
induction s as [| l IHl o r IHr]; simpl.
Lemma min_elt_spec3: forall s, min_elt s = None -> Empty s.
induction s as [|l IHl o r IHr].
Lemma min_elt_spec2: forall s x y, min_elt s = Some x -> In y s -> ~ E.lt y x.
induction s as [|l IHl o r IHr]; intros x y H H'.
destruct y as [z|z|]; simpl; intro; trivial.
intro Hp; rewrite Hp in H.
Lemma max_elt_spec1: forall s x, max_elt s = Some x -> In x s.
induction s as [| l IHl o r IHr]; simpl.
Lemma max_elt_spec3: forall s, max_elt s = None -> Empty s.
induction s as [|l IHl o r IHr].
Lemma max_elt_spec2: forall s x y, max_elt s = Some x -> In y s -> ~ E.lt x y.
induction s as [|l IHl o r IHr]; intros x y H H'.
destruct y as [z|z|]; simpl; intro; trivial.
intro Hp; rewrite Hp in H.
